00:30:28,432 --> 00:30:30,183
Allyson?

615
00:30:43,897 --> 00:30:45,796
Alô?

616
00:30:45,832 --> 00:30:47,660
Allyson.

617
00:30:47,696 --> 00:30:48,781
Foi...

618
00:30:48,817 --> 00:30:49,828
